      "content": "wait, \"the only issue we're aware of\"? that's not exactly what i needed to hear. if there are any stability issues at all, even if they seem \"isolated,\" i need a full list of them before i sign off on this. are you absolutely sure there aren't any intermittent crashes or session-ending bugs hiding in the most recent stress test data? i don't want to find out about a 5% crash rate on launch day after you told me we were good.",
